10:30:02 INFO  KafkaConsumer - Retry 1/3 for notification: abc-123 (wait 1s)
10:30:04 INFO  KafkaConsumer - Retry 2/3 for notification: abc-123 (wait 2s)
10:30:08 INFO  KafkaConsumer - Retry 3/3 for notification: abc-123 (wait 4s)
10:30:12 WARN  KafkaConsumer - All retries exhausted. Moving to DLQ: notifications.failed
```

